    "description": "Chessplosion是一款街机动作解谜游戏——放置棋子炸弹，制造连锁爆炸困住敌人。在冒险模式和由roguelike启发的地城模式中打败敌人和头目，在解谜模式中用有限的炸弹消灭目标，在对战模式中与朋友或电脑对战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571220/extras/8d46cafdf69b346ef2108ee832139590.poster.avif?t=1745588070\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571220/extras/8d46cafdf69b346ef2108ee832139590.webm?t=1745588070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571220/extras/8d46cafdf69b346ef2108ee832139590.mp4?t=1745588070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在冒险模式中打败一系列敌人和头目，其灵感来自于国际象棋棋子的行棋方式。躲避冲锋的车，小心象的斜向射线，还要提防马的铁蹄！<br><br>在地城模式中勇闯随机生成的地城，在寻找棋圣之冠的路上打败敌人，积攒金钱。大量的强力升级和武器意味着每一次冒险都与众不同！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571220/extras/3cb231df38b3dd96b0204acbb11dc254.poster.avif?t=1745588070\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571220/extras/3cb231df38b3dd96b0204acbb11dc254.webm?t=1745588070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571220/extras/3cb231df38b3dd96b0204acbb11dc254.mp4?t=1745588070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在解谜模式中解决超过100道谜题，用有限的炸弹制造连锁爆炸消灭目标。还可以用谜题编辑器创造自己的谜题，分享给朋友们！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571220/extras/11a2ebf181938e6d0a9cb4a063a80a16.poster.avif?t=1745588070\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571220/extras/11a2ebf181938e6d0a9cb4a063a80a16.webm?t=1745588070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571220/extras/11a2ebf181938e6d0a9cb4a063a80a16.mp4?t=1745588070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在生存模式中躲避炸弹，在一波波凶险的轰炸中闪躲腾挪。游戏的开始并不难，但到了结尾你要面对的可是诸如王后弹幕的挑战，神机妙算和当机立断二者缺一不可。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571220/extras/8dc9cf9c622ebaed2f1c7d89ff014b63.poster.avif?t=1745588070\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571220/extras/8dc9cf9c622ebaed2f1c7d89ff014b63.webm?t=1745588070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571220/extras/8dc9cf9c622ebaed2f1c7d89ff014b63.mp4?t=1745588070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在对战模式中与电脑或其他玩家对弈，线上和本地均可多人游戏。若是想要试试比通常的混战和团队战更新鲜的，可以在网球模式中将炸弹扔过中线，制造连锁爆炸让你的对手躲避。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏内容</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在冒险模式中面对8个头目和超过90个关卡。<br></li><li>在地城模式中探索随机生成的地下城。<br></li><li>在解谜模式中解开超过100个谜题，或是创造自己的谜题分享给朋友。<br></li><li>在生存模式中顶住超过10个关卡的轰炸。<br></li><li>在对战模式的20余个战场中与朋友对战；线上或本地多人游戏允许至多4名玩家参与。<br></li><li>用简单易懂的辅助模式随心调整游戏难度，改变生命值、复活次数和游戏速度，甚至直接跳过卡住的关卡。</li></ul>",
